# ── Committed assets for dashboard demo ──
# dashboard_assets/ is intentionally tracked — it contains a snapshot
# of the processed data (~4.8 MB) and trained model (~1.3 MB) so the
# Streamlit dashboard works immediately after cloning without running
# notebooks or training scripts first.